title: Files > Document and Others ; What does the Kaomoji tab do?
content:
I've been trying to get custom kaomojis on the google keyboard by using stuff like dictionary shortcuts and whatnot but it didn't work. Was looking through my Files to clear up storage and found the Documents and others section has a Kaomoji tab with and empty storage.txt
Is there any way to use this to get custom kaomojis on the google keyboard? Or is this leftover from a kaomoji app I downloaded and I should delete it?
